Package pdb.model.spatial

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Entity
    Class Entity represents entity and its values - lake, house etc Can generate shapes from its geometry
    Estate
    Class Estate represents estates and its values Can generate shapes from its geometry
    ImprovedCircle
    Class ImprovedCircle represents circles with extra reference to Entity by which it was created
    ImprovedPath
    Class ImprovedPath represents paths with extra reference to Entity by which it was created
    ImprovedPolygon
    Class ImprovedPolygon represents polygon with extra reference to Entity by which it was created
    Shapes
    Class Shapes represents lists of ImprovedCircles, ImprovedPaths, ImprovedPolygons
    ShapesColorsDefinition
    Class which contains color definition (stroke and fill) for all spatial entities which are drawed onto map
    SpatialEntitiesModel
    Class SpatialEntitiesModel database model for Spatial entities Contains all the DB work for spatial entities
    SpatialEntity
    Class which is inherited in other spatial entities
    SpatialModel
    Class which do backend operations for SpatialPaneController
